    "headline": "LKQ Corporation to Release Second Quarter 2026 Results on Thursday, July 30, 2026",
    "summary": "ANTIOCH, Tenn., July 02, 2026 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- LKQ Corporation (Nasdaq: LKQ) will release its second quarter 2026 financial results on Thursday, July 30, 2026. Conference Call Details LKQ will host a conference call and webcast on July 30, 2026 at 8:00 a.m. Eastern Time (7:00 a.m. Central Time) with members of senior management to discuss the Company's results. To access the investor conference call, please dial (833) 461-5787. International access to the call may be obtained by dialing (626)",
